@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wuexio(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.abs(tmp) / (wp.sin(v2 + 0.39) + v0))
    v2 = v0
    tmp = (v2 - wp.sin(v2))
    v0 = ((tmp + (tmp + 0.36 - v1 + 0.47)) + (tmp + wp.abs(tmp + 0.32)))
    tmp = tmp
    v2 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.43 * v1 + 0.91)) - wp.sin(0.24))
    data[tid] = v0
